latestPosts.caption:
SKIN

Taking care of your skin is essential. Its starts with what you put in your body. Hydration is key to clear, plump skin. As is having a skin care routine. Always remove your makeup at night, oil cleansing is a great way to keep skin hydrated as your remove  makeup, dirt and impurities.  I did the beautiful @iamoliviagolden makeup for this @maccosmetics shoot. Here she is wearing a sheer layer of #faceandbodyfoundation its my fav go to for gorgeous believable skin. 
#maccosmetics #macmyday #macartglam #macseniorartistna #seniorartistglam #skin #healthyskin #glowyskin #skinsecrets
